snippet.title: Solitaire: Decked Out (Classic Klondike Card Game)
snippet.description:
Solitaire: Decked Out is now available to download in
App Store: https://goo.gl/oeixIi
Google Play Store: https://goo.gl/31TWcI

We’ve taken classic solitaire and remastered it. Solitaire: Decked Out features funny decks and decorative items. By unlocking decks and items, players can collect interactive effects and animated winning ceremonies.
